  "text": "were measured in duplicate using a radioassay procedure based on [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] . A 7% human albumin solution was used as zero folate standard. Serum was first diluted 1:10 with this solution, and analyses were performed using the Bio-Rad Quantaphase Folate Kit 7 and a gamma counter s. The count of the folate standards were expressed as B/Bo 9 plotted on a threecycle log-logit paper to obtain a straight standard curve.",
